invalid type: string "He could destroy the entire universe!\nDid they call him?\nApocalyptic canyon!\nTo get it moving, they needed...\nThe most powerful princess in the universe!\nAnd once they extracted all its power,\nAnd the weapon was ready...\nThey traveled from planet to\\Nplanet, destroying everything...\nthe one who had disrespected them.\n¡Boom!\n¡Boom!\nUntil they danced on the ashes!